{"tid":922581,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"MODEM / ROUTER / 上網求教","createTime":"2018-11-30T13:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T07:58:03.000Z","uid":31796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"73c368acd7f708270fac453181db3f7fc706b998","tid":922581,"uid":31796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T13:21:26.000Z","msg":"尋日開始上網有問題<br />\n用緊WIFI ROUTER WAN粒燈紅色, 即係唔正常<br />\n電腦上唔到網, SHOW左下面呢一句<br />\nDNS_PROBE_FINISHED_NO_INTERNET<br />\n試過MODEM直插電腦, 唔得<br />\n試過熄晒D野再插D線, 唔得<br />\n試過換LAN線, 又唔得<br />\n<br />\n我隔左一日再返黎試<br />\n奇怪在我首先開PS4同電話係連到機同埋用到WIFI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我一開電腦連線又用唔返<br />\n用電腦試完之後電話都連唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我用電話數據SHARE WIFI俾電腦, 電腦係可以正常上網<br />\n即係唔係電腦問題<br />\n<br />\n打俾PCCW又話見到我有裝置連到線即係唔關佢地事<br />\n我問請教下有冇高手可以幫我解決下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185248957c76f3d8ad5f2aca5b7e5ffc4dd96d78","tid":922581,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21354afef99518444efe605adfb1ae5689db43cc","tid":922581,"uid":31796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T13:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb97e64a9f302268127b181ec54f11ef21e2bf1","tid":922581,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T13:36:56.000Z","msg":"係咪未set DNS"},{"pid":"e22153c134c3006087965972d0c4a44e40164220","tid":922581,"uid":180127,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"185248957c76f3d8ad5f2aca5b7e5ffc4dd96d78","tid":922581,"uid":21423,"like":